This special parameterization was used to investigate Sulfur
passivated GaAs surface reconstructions. It was also used to study
the adsorption of PTCDA on GaAs, Silver and Silicon surfaces.

The files have been updated to allow for TD-DFTB calculations.

 Relevant Publications
----------------------

- B. Szuecs, Z. Hajnal, T. Frauenheim, C. Gonzales, J. Ortega,
R. Perez, and F. Flores, Appl.Surf.Sci., vol. 212, p. 861, 2003.

- B. Szuecs, Z. Hajnal, R. Scholz, S. Sanna, and T. Frauenheim
Appl.Surf.Sci., vol. 234, pp. 173-177, 2004.


